<emphasis id="0FA2AC65462B4B11BB047BC509BA563C" italics="true" pageId="111" pageNumber="112">tayaw</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="5EC49D893CD259B05450FD03EB2A48D9" bold="true" pageId="111" pageNumber="112">English</emphasis>
