</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="3B886C80D09C57417645A64141706CA5" pageId="111" pageNumber="112" type="range">
<paragraph id="D112C32DDB94D87DF9AD321C8DB0F7A9" pageId="111" pageNumber="112">Range.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C147DC5D6666A2569768D325DA8ACDA4" pageId="111" pageNumber="112">China, Bangladesh, Cambodia, India, Laos, Malaysia, Myanmar, Nepal, Sri Lanka, Thailand, and Vietnam. In Myanmar, found in Bago, Mandalay, and Shan.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
